{
  "_comment": [
    "Effective redox-onset model for the existing EC/DMC electrolyte system.",
    "This file is intended for estimating reduction onset within the present",
    "coarse-grained RedoxMC model, not for final ab initio thermochemistry.",
    "",
    "Literature-inspired targets used here:",
    "  EC reduction onset  ~ 0.47 V vs Li/Li+  -> about -0.93 V vs vacuum",
    "  DMC reduction onset ~ 0.38 V vs Li/Li+  -> about -1.02 V vs vacuum",
    "",
    "To represent those onset voltages in the current model, we use direct",
    "state_free_energy_offsets_kjmol instead of gas-phase EA placeholders.",
    "At DeltaG(V)=offset + F*V, the crossing occurs when V = -offset/F."
  ],
